snippet.title: Knightmare Tower - Gameplay footage (beta)
snippet.description:
Very first gameplay footage from Knightmare Tower, the upcoming Juicy Beast game! Note that this is not final and that there's a lot of missing elements/unfinished visuals.

Visit http://www.juicybeast.com for more info on the game and the release date.

Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/juicybeast
Twitter: https://twitter.com/juicybeast
Google+: https://plus.google.com/108157607990849336850/
